.TH "LIGHTNING-SEND" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-send \- keysend a payment to a raw node id (no invoice)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning send
[\fIsubcommand\fR] [\fIargs\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.nf
lightning send — keysend a payment to a raw node id (no invoice).

Implements: keysend (BOLT-4 + TLV records) per FEAT-173.
  share/doc/lightning/standards/bolts/04-onion-routing.md

Usage:
  lightning send <node-id> <sat> [--message <text>]
                                 [--account <name>]
                                 [--note <text>]
.fi
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR lightning (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Part of the \fBlightning\fR educational Lightning Network frontend.
